## Phase 2: ELK Stack (Elasticsearch, Logstash, Kibana)

**Amaç:** Tüm servislerden merkezi log toplama, indeksleme ve görselleştirme.

### Mimari

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[auth-service] -->|logs| F[Filebeat]
    B[user-service] -->|logs| F
    C[game-service] -->|logs| F
    D[nginx] -->|logs| F
    F -->|forward| L[Logstash]
    L -->|index| E[Elasticsearch]
    E -->|query| K[Kibana]
```

### Yapılacaklar

#### [NEW] [elk/elasticsearch/elasticsearch.yml](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/elk/elasticsearch/elasticsearch.yml)
- Single-node cluster yapılandırması
- Bellek limitleri (512MB heap)
- Data retention politikası (ILM - Index Lifecycle Management)
- Güvenlik ayarları (xpack security)

#### [NEW] [elk/logstash/logstash.conf](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/elk/logstash/logstash.conf)
- Input: Filebeat'ten gelen log verileri (port 5044)
- Filter: JSON parse, timestamp düzenleme, grok patterns
- Output: Elasticsearch'e indeksleme
- Farklı servisler için ayrı index pattern'ları

#### [NEW] [elk/logstash/pipeline/](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/elk/logstash/pipeline/)
- `auth-logs.conf`: Auth servisi log pipeline
- `access-logs.conf`: Nginx access log pipeline
- `app-logs.conf`: Uygulama logları pipeline

#### [NEW] [elk/kibana/kibana.yml](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/elk/kibana/kibana.yml)
- Elasticsearch bağlantı ayarları
- Güvenlik ayarları
- Default dashboard import

#### [NEW] [elk/filebeat/filebeat.yml](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/elk/filebeat/filebeat.yml)
- Docker container log toplama
- Multiline log desteği
- Her servis için etiketleme

### Docker Compose Eklentileri

```yaml
# ELK servisleri docker-compose.yml'e eklenecek
elasticsearch:
  image: docker.elastic.co/elasticsearch/elasticsearch:8.11.0
  environment:
    - discovery.type=single-node
    - ES_JAVA_OPTS=-Xms512m -Xmx512m
    - xpack.security.enabled=true
  volumes:
    - es_data:/usr/share/elasticsearch/data
  ports:
    - "9200:9200"

logstash:
  image: docker.elastic.co/logstash/logstash:8.11.0
  volumes:
    - ./elk/logstash/pipeline:/usr/share/logstash/pipeline
  depends_on:
    - elasticsearch

kibana:
  image: docker.elastic.co/kibana/kibana:8.11.0
  ports:
    - "5601:5601"
  depends_on:
    - elasticsearch

filebeat:
  image: docker.elastic.co/beats/filebeat:8.11.0
  volumes:
    - /var/lib/docker/containers:/var/lib/docker/containers:ro
    - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock:ro
```

### Data Retention Politikası
- **Hot phase**: Son 7 gün (SSD, hızlı arama)
- **Warm phase**: 7-30 gün (daha az kaynak)
- **Delete phase**: 30 gün sonra otomatik silme

### Güvenlik
- Elasticsearch xpack.security etkin
- Kibana'ya kullanıcı/şifre ile erişim
- HTTPS üzerinden iletişim (internal network)

---

## Phase 3: Prometheus + Grafana (İzleme Sistemi)

**Amaç:** Tüm sistem bileşenlerinin performans ve sağlık metriklerini toplamak ve görselleştirmek.

### Mimari

```mermaid
graph TD
    P[Prometheus] -->|scrape| NE[Node Exporter]
    P -->|scrape| CA[cAdvisor]
    P -->|scrape| AS[auth-service /metrics]
    P -->|scrape| US[user-service /metrics]
    P -->|scrape| GS[game-service /metrics]
    P -->|scrape| NX[Nginx Exporter]
    P -->|alert| AM[Alertmanager]
    G[Grafana] -->|query| P
```

### Yapılacaklar

#### [NEW] [monitoring/prometheus/prometheus.yml](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/monitoring/prometheus/prometheus.yml)
- Scrape config: Her servis için `/metrics` endpoint
- Scrape interval: 15 saniye
- Alert rules import

#### [NEW] [monitoring/prometheus/alert.rules.yml](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/monitoring/prometheus/alert.rules.yml)
- **HighCPU**: CPU kullanımı > %80 → uyarı
- **HighMemory**: Bellek kullanımı > %80 → uyarı
- **ServiceDown**: Herhangi bir servis çökmesi → kritik
- **HighErrorRate**: HTTP 5xx oranı > %5 → uyarı
- **HighLatency**: Yanıt süresi > 1s → uyarı

#### [NEW] [monitoring/grafana/provisioning/datasources/prometheus.yml](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/monitoring/grafana/provisioning/datasources/prometheus.yml)
- Prometheus veri kaynağı otomatik yapılandırma

#### [NEW] [monitoring/grafana/provisioning/dashboards/](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/monitoring/grafana/provisioning/dashboards/)
- `system-overview.json`: CPU, memory, disk, network
- `docker-containers.json`: Container metrikleri
- `http-overview.json`: Request rate, latency, error rate
- `service-health.json`: Her servisin sağlık durumu

#### Uygulama Metrikleri (Her Mikroservise)
- `prom-client` npm paketi ile Fastify'a metrik endpoint ekleme
- Request count, duration, error rate metrikleri
- Custom business metrikleri (aktif kullanıcılar, maç sayısı vb.)

### Docker Compose Eklentileri

```yaml
prometheus:
  image: prom/prometheus:v2.48.0
  volumes:
    - ./monitoring/prometheus:/etc/prometheus
    - prometheus_data:/prometheus
  ports:
    - "9090:9090"
  command:
    - '--config.file=/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml'
    - '--storage.tsdb.retention.time=30d'

grafana:
  image: grafana/grafana:10.2.0
  volumes:
    - ./monitoring/grafana/provisioning:/etc/grafana/provisioning
    - grafana_data:/var/lib/grafana
  ports:
    - "3001:3000"
  environment:
    - GF_SECURITY_ADMIN_USER=admin
    - GF_SECURITY_ADMIN_PASSWORD=${GRAFANA_ADMIN_PASSWORD}
    - GF_AUTH_ANONYMOUS_ENABLED=false

node-exporter:
  image: prom/node-exporter:v1.7.0
  volumes:
    - /proc:/host/proc:ro
    - /sys:/host/sys:ro

cadvisor:
  image: gcr.io/cadvisor/cadvisor:v0.47.2
  volumes:
    - /:/rootfs:ro
    - /var/run:/var/run:ro
    - /sys:/sys:ro
    - /var/lib/docker/:/var/lib/docker:ro
  ports:
    - "8080:8080"
```

### Grafana Güvenlik
- Admin şifre [.env](file:///home/gumusay/Desktop/ft_transcendence/ft_transcendence-backend/backend/.env) dosyasından
- Anonim erişim kapalı
- Viewer/Editor/Admin rol yönetimi

### Veri Saklama
- Prometheus: 30 gün retention
- Grafana: Persistent volume ile kalıcı dashboard

